Friends, we opened our patreon https://www.patreon.com/voices_org_ua

Patrons and patronesses, join us to make good things together. We make all possible not to leave any child in Ukraine alone with his war trauma.

Due to your support:
- we give psychological help to children and parents, who suffered in the war;
- we urgently help women and children - refugees from the Ukrainian lands with the essentials, house and moving;
- we create studying platforms for children, which were evacuated from the shootings;
- we make individual help to families with children who suffered in the war.

Together we can overcome all and in all cases!!!

